{"tid":927108,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"又葡萄！C朗失金球獎 又搵家姐出動","createTime":"2018-12-04T02:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T03:44:44.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ac007ab1065b057ad86e15f6d401ab712c1de499","tid":927108,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=woWKBtP6PCnvw6rWWJT%2B2vM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=03c30116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】早前基斯坦奴朗拿度失落歐洲足協最佳球員，他的二家姐Katia已在instagram上發功替細佬不值，周一C朗又失落金球獎，Katia就聯同大家姐Elma齊齊發聲。<br />\n<br />\n「很無奈，現在這個世界就是這樣，是如此的腐敗，充斥黑手黨與他X的金錢。但上帝的力量能戰勝這一切腐敗。若然未報，只因為時辰未到。」大家姐Elma在instagram上說，連上帝與黑手黨都牽扯進來，實在令人摸不著頭腦。 Katia跟大家姐一樣，甫上基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）過去得獎的威水相，評語就精警得多：「這位就是世界上最佳球員&mdash;&mdash;當然只限於在識波的人眼中。」 對兩姊妹的一唱一和，有網民不以為然：「C朗今年得票第2。你們（兩姊妹）這樣糾纏下去，實在很小家。」今屆金球獎周一揭曉，莫迪歷以大熱姿態奪獎，結束了C朗、美斯的10年壟斷局面。"},{"pid":"2724eadf7921220584afd255d38326a54d563f4f","tid":927108,"uid":196924,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:53:03.000Z","msg":"有名你叫葡萄牙朗"},{"pid":"56300f9fde0c66449cc59f3c83e9bddae264b318","tid":927108,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2724eadf7921220584afd255d38326a54d563f4f","tid":927108,"uid":196924,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:53:03.000Z","msg":"有名你叫葡萄牙朗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:54:21.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff5d73cb1c6348ec124fd076f7cc861f176feb1","tid":927108,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a23df17064d29dad35988eb8d848902eb97e6a3","tid":927108,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03:44:44.000Z","msg":"豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cla